OL,3,CKing Charles brings British soft power
OL,4,Cto America
OL,6,FThere is a tree King Charles planted
OL,7,Fin the surroundings of the British
OL,8,FEmbassy Gardens in 2005, which is now
OL,9,Fspreading into a mature specimen.
OL,11,FThe London Maple was a reminder of the
OL,12,Fpassage of time for the Monarch, who
OL,13,Fput it in the ground on his first
OL,14,Fjoint overseas official visit more
OL,15,Fthan two decades ago.
OL,17,FAs he and the Queen greeted the elite
OL,18,Fof Washington last night, the roots of
OL,19,Fshared culture and history appeared as
OL,20,Fhealthy as that sapling.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
