OL,3,CKing Charles brings British soft power
OL,4,Cto America
OL,6,FFrom the Speaker of the House of
OL,7,FRepresentatives, to Senator Ted Cruz,
OL,8,Fthe Trump loyalists were queuing up
OL,9,F(or lining up as they say here) for a
OL,10,Fmoment with their Majesties.
OL,12,FIt was a potent display of British
OL,13,Fsoft power.
OL,15,FIn the 250th year after the United
OL,16,FStates broke with the monarchy,
OL,17,FAmerica couldn't get enough of it.
OL,19,FI watched as King Charles and Queen
OL,20,FCamilla worked the crowd seamlessly.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
