OL,3,CKing Charles brings British soft power
OL,4,Cto America
OL,6,FAt one point, King Charles stopped
OL,7,Fnear me and shook my hand. We
OL,8,Fexchanged pleasantries and a joke,
OL,9,Fbefore he glided on.
OL,11,FHis ability to charm and connect in a
OL,12,Ffew short seconds was impressive,
OL,13,Fbeguiling the gathered power-couples,
OL,14,Fcabinet members, movers and shakers
OL,15,Fwith ease.
OL,17,FRelations between Sir Keir Starmer and
OL,18,FPresident Trump may be strained, but
OL,19,Fit appeared for a moment the magic of
OL,20,Fmonarchy has transcended all political
OL,21,Ftensions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/4
